comments: As Payton II (GSW) goes under the pick, Gobert (UTA) makes marginal contact and doesn't affect Payton II's ability to contest the shot attempt.
Payton II (GSW) is firming up in Conley's (UTA) path when marginal body contact occurs on the off-ball screen.
Porter Jr. (GSW) and Bogdanovic (UTA) both engage and separate off-ball.
Wiggins (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position as he cleanly dislodges the ball from Mitchell (UTA).
Wiggins (GSW) dislodges the ball out of bounds. Possession correctly remains with UTA.
Curry (GSW) moves into Mitchell (UTA) with his forearm and makes contact before Mitchell begins his upward shooting motion.
O'Neale (UTA) gathers on his right foot and takes one step before passing.
Looney (GSW) jumps from point A to point B and dislodges O'Neale (UTA) from his position.
Porter Jr. (GSW) and Bogdanovic (UTA) engage and separate during the made shot attempt.
Iguodala (GSW) dislodges the incoming pass out of bounds. Possession correctly remains with UTA.
Mitchell (UTA) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Mitchell (UTA) reaches out of bounds and makes contact with the ball while it is in Iguodala's (GSW) hands during the inbound.
All Technical Fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Gobert (UTA) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Wiggins (GSW) legally contests Mitchell's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
